'''地区主义'''（{{lang-en|Regionalism}}）是一种政治[[意識形態|意識形態]]<ref>{{Cite journal|jstor = 422257|title = A Rational Choice Approach to Political Regionalism|url = https://archive.org/details/sim_comparative-politics_1991-07_23_4/page/401|journal = Comparative Politics|volume = 23|issue = 4|pages = 401–421|last1 = Meadwell|first1 = Hudson|year = 1991|doi = 10.2307/422257}}</ref>，含有三种不同的要素：要求在统一国家内实行地区自治的运动；国家以地区为基础组织起来执行其政策，包括地区发展政策；[[权力下放|权力下放]]和[[地方分权|地区自治]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://pesd.princeton.edu/?q=node/264|title=The Princeton Encyclopedia of Self-Determination|website=pesd.princeton.edu|access-date=2022-03-16|archive-date=2021-10-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211025194405/https://pesd.princeton.edu/?q=node%2F264|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

